接口 net.rubyeye.xmemcached.CommandFactory
的使用

使用 CommandFactory 的软件包
net.rubyeye.xmemcached XMemcached's main classes and interfaces,use these classes/interfaces to interact with memcached servers. 
net.rubyeye.xmemcached.auth Memcached 1.4.3 or later version has supported SASL authentication,these classes are used for that  
net.rubyeye.xmemcached.command Memcached protocol implementations 
net.rubyeye.xmemcached.impl Manage tcp connection,memcached protocol optimized,and some MBeans for monitor. 
net.rubyeye.xmemcached.utils XMemcached Utilities 
net.rubyeye.xmemcached.utils.hibernate Hibernate-memcached supports

net.rubyeye.xmemcached.command 中 CommandFactory 的使用
 

实现 CommandFactory 的 net.rubyeye.xmemcached.command 中的类
 class BinaryCommandFactory
          Binary protocol command factory
 class KestrelCommandFactory
          Kestrel is a message queue written in scala by robey(http://github.com/robey/kestrel).It's protocol use memcached text protocol,so you can use any memcached clients to talk with it.But it's protocol implementation is not all compatible with memcached standard protocol,So xmemcached supply this command factory for it.
 class TextCommandFactory
          Command Factory for creating text protocol commands.
